dct_title_s: The British Isles : comprehending Great Britain and Ireland with The Adjacent Islands
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially.   "London : printed for Rob't Sayer, No.53 in Fleet Street as the Act directed 10 Jan. 1774."   Appears to be a two page spread removed from a book. "4" in corners on bottom outside neat line, as a page number.
Scale approximately 1:2,926.000. 100 Statute miles 69 1/2 au Degree = 5,5 cm
